-- Pan African Resources Agrees to Build a Chrome Tailings Retreatment Plant
-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 2010-11-05T09:23:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-05/pan-african-resources-in-pact-to-build-chrome-tailings-retreatment-plant.html
Pan African Resources Plc said it
signed an agreement with International Ferro Metals SA Ltd. that
will enable its Phoenix Platinum Mining Ltd. unit to build a
chrome tailings retreatment plant.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  